\c 45
\s Ihubo elihayelwa inkosi lomakoti wayo
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela, ngeShoshanimi, esamadodana kaKora, Masikili, ingoma yezintando
\p
\v 1 Inhliziyo yami iphuphuma ngendaba enhle; ngikhuluma ngezinto engizenzele inkosi; ulimi lwami lulusiba\x + Jobe 19.24. Jer. 8.8. 17.1.\x* lombhali ophangisayo\x + Ezra 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Umuhle kulabantwana babantu; umusa uthululwe endebeni zakho; ngenxa yalokho uNkulunkulu ukubusisile kuze kube phakade\x + Luka 4.22.\x*.
\v 3 Bhinca inkemba yakho\x + Isam. 1.16.\x* emlenzeni\x + Eks. 32.27.\x*, qhawe\x + Isa. 9.6.\x*, udumo lwakho lobukhosi bakho\x + Hlab. 21.5.\x*.
\v 4 Lebukhosini bakho gada uphumulele, ngenxa yeqiniso lobumnene bokulunga\x + Isam. 6.2.\x*; lesandla sakho sokunene sikufundise izinto ezesabekayo\x + Hlab. 65.5.\x*.
\v 5 Imitshoko yakho ibukhali enhliziyweni yezitha zenkosi; izizwe zizakuwa ngaphansi kwakho\x + Hlab. 120.4. Zaga 25.18. Isa. 5.28.\x*.
\v 6 Isihlalo sakho sobukhosi, Nkulunkulu, ngesaphakade laphakade; intonga yakho yobukhosi iyintonga yobuqotho\x + Hlab. 93.2. Heb. 1.8,9. Hlab. 110.2. Zaga 8.22.\x*.
\v 7 Uthanda ukulunga, njalo uzonda ububi\x + Hlab. 11.7.\x*; ngenxa yalokho uNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Isa. 61.1.\x*, ukugcobile\x + 1 Kho. 1.39,40. Hlab. 2.2.\x* ngamafutha entokozo ngaphezu kwabanakwenu\x + Hlab. 21.6.\x*.
\v 8 Izembatho zakho zonke \add ziqholiwe\add* \w ngemure\w**\x + Joha. 19.39.\x* lenhlaba \w \add l\add*ekhasiya\w**\x + Joha. 19.39.\x*; ezigodlweni zempondo zendlovu abakwenze wathokoza ngazo.
\v 9 Amadodakazi amakhosi aphakathi kwabesifazana bakho abadumileyo\x + 45.14.\x*; indlovukazi\x + Neh. 2.6.\x* imi esandleni sokunene sakho\x + 1 Kho. 2.19. Mat. 25.34.\x* yembethe igolide\x + Jobe 28.16.\x* leOfiri\x + 1 Kho. 9.28.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zwana, ndodakazi, unakane, ubeke indlebe yakho; ukhohlwe abantu bakini lendlu kayihlo\x + Dute. 21.13.\x*;
\v 11 khona inkosi izalangatha ubuhle bakho; ngoba iyinkosi yakho\x + Isa. 51.22.\x*, njalo khothama kuyo\x + Hlab. 95.6. Isa. 54.5.\x*.
\v 12 Lendodakazi yeTire ilesipho\x + Hlab. 96.8. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*, labanothileyo ebantwini, bazancenga ubuso bakho\x + Hlab. 22.29. 68.29. 72.10. Isa. 49.7,23. Mat. 2.11.\x*.
\v 13 Indodakazi yenkosi iyakhazimula yonke\x + Jobe 20.26.\x* ngaphakathi, isembatho sayo singesegolide elelukiweyo\x + Levi 10.18. 1 Kho. 6.18.\x*.
\v 14 Izalethwa enkosini\x + Isam. 19.7,8.\x* yembethe isembatho esifekethisiweyo\x + 2 Sam. 13.18.\x*; izintombi eziyilandelayo, abangane bayo, zizalethwa kuwe.
\v 15 Zizalethwa ngokuthaba lenjabulo, zizangena esigodlweni senkosi.
\v 16 Esikhundleni saboyihlo kuzakuba ngamadodana akho, uzawabeka abe yiziphathamandla emhlabeni wonke\x + 1 Pet. 2.9. Isam. 1.6. 5.10. 20.6. 22.5.\x*.
\v 17 Ibizo lakho ngizalenza likhunjulwe ezizukulwaneni zonke\x + Hlab. 10.6.\x*; ngenxa yalokho izizwe zizakudumisa kuze kube nini lanini.
